title: Bug 114470[Smoke] Error message throws when using new Date('3/2/2005') as value in table filter.
OB: Error message is thrown when attempting to use the date '3/2/2005' as a value in a table filter.
EB: The system should allow using the date '3/2/2005' as a value in a table filter without throwing an error message.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the table filter.
2. Enter the value '3/2/2005' as a date.
3. Apply the filter and observe the error message that is thrown.
